data.description:
Welcome Home to this Nicely Updated Split Level Home! As you enter, you will view
the Beautiful Bay Window in the Open Living Room! You walk over to the Dining Room
with Awesome Chandelier and then step into the Inviting Kitchen! This Kitchen boasts
Granite Countertops, Subway Tile, Ceramic Tile Floors and More! The Refrigerator,
Stove, Microwave and Dishwasher all Stay! You proceed Upstairs to the Updated Full
Bath with Laminate Floors and the 3 Carpeted Bedrooms! Then you walk down to the
Spacious Family Room and a 2nd Updated Full Bath with Vinyl Laminate Floors! The
Large Laundry Room is on this level also with the Washer and Dryer to Stay! There is
an Extra Large Storage Bench that will remain too! This Laundry Room leads to the
Attached 2 Car Garage! This Fantastic Garage offers New Concrete Floor with Epoxy
Paint, Insulation, Drywall and a New Side Door! There is also extra Attic Storage! As
you walk back up to the Kitchen, you step out the Sliding Door to the Covered Patio
installed in 2022! This Yard is fully Chain link Fenced - 2022 and includes a Shed!
There is a New Roof (Full Tear Off) - 2022! New Gutters and Downspouts - 2022! The
Front Driveway has 2 New Slabs also! This Great Home is within walking distance of
an Elementary School and close to lots of Shopping! Come and See this Beauty
before it's gone!
